{"tid":2385401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★大摩CEO：Reddit上的股民將會遭到「當頭棒喝」","createTime":"2021-01-29T04:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T01:59:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"516141cf8693d8efa36845132c8cdaad3a0ac3d5","tid":2385401,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"彭博】-- 摩根士丹利執行長James Gorman認為，Reddit上的叛逆股民炒作小眾股刺激大盤震盪，將會遭遇難受的意外。<br />\n<br />\n「這裡有些人必遭當頭棒喝，」Gorman在沙烏地阿拉伯的未來投資倡議大會上說。「我不知道是明天、下周還是下個月，但終會發生。」<br />\n<br />\n摩根士丹利去年收購了E*Trade Financial Corp.，進一步涉足散戶交易領域。Gorman說，他仍然認為這筆交易對摩根士丹利是個巨大的勝利，E*Trade新增賬戶數量去年提高了3倍。<br />\n<br />\n他說，散戶抱團軋空是個「短期現象」，「不會持久。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9ceo-reddit%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E8%82%A1%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%83%E9%81%AD%E5%88%B0-%E7%95%B6%E9%A0%AD%E6%A3%92%E5%96%9D-150340525.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2591%25A9%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E4%25B8%25B9%25E5%2588%25A9ceo-reddit%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25A3%2592%25E5%2596%259D-150340525.html&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=74d70d06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9ceo-reddit%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E8%82%A1%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%83%E9%81%AD%E5%88%B0-%E7%95%B6%E9%A0%AD%E6%A3%92%E5%96%9D-150340525.html</a>"},{"pid":"4f7b1c2863717013737e0d7c09b6cfa11d36ee9e","tid":2385401,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"h